Name: Kz NTools : Fix Your Network
About the game: What is Kz NTools ? Kz NTools is a powerfull network tool. Developed by person who hates high ping. Kz Ntools will ease your connection and help to fix your issues. Features Just click one button and lay back (Reset your firewall settings, clear DNS cache and some magical tricks) :) Low memory usage Wi-Fi Hotspot Support Non-Steam Games Too :) Show and manage DNS records. And of course we have extras for you :) Extras Shutdown and Restart Options Shutdown and Restart Timers Change and Reset DNS Turn your network connection on/off
